features: ❤Roinvou dashcam comes with a 32GB memory card and two small crowbars for installation.❤

🚗One-hand Operation Touch Screen: Designed with 4.0 inch sensitive touch screen, the dash cam front and rear view allows you not to operate with pressing buttons anymore. It is specially designed to offer you effortless operation and optimal using feeling. You are allowed do all the operations with only one finger, such as navigate to the Menu settings, take a snapshot, lock video files manually or playback videos.

🚗Loop Recording & Audio Recording: The dash camera for cars comes with loop recording, new recordings will automatically overwrite oldest recordings when the memory card is full. Built in microphone and speaker to capture high quality audio clear without distortion. Don't want to record voice? Just one press to turn the microphone off.

🚗24 Hours Parking Monitor & G-sensor: The backup camera for car dashboard can monitor your car condition for 24 hours with continuous power supply. Parking mode monitors your car’s surroundings when you are away for a vacation or leaving your car for quite some time. The G-sensor with auto collision detection will detect impacts and lock important video segments to the emergency files folder and prevent overwriting of your video file.

🚗150° Wide Angle Lens: The 150°(1080P) wide-angle front and 120°(720P) rear car dash camera covers up to 4 lanes of traffic, which helps captures more of the road around you. This ensures a panoramic recording , never miss an event ahead, beside or to the rear of your vehicle while minimizing distortion. The Roinvou car recorder camera is meant to record evidence of any incident involving your vehicle, or even just record some nice scenery along the way.

🚗Super Clear Night Vision with WDR/HDR Technology: Both front and rear camera is loaded with super high quality sensor which has better night vision than any other sensors. Wide Dynamic Range technology, provide clearer view than most other car cameras in low-light conditions for nighttime driving. HDR technology helps to retain details in high contrast light, which means even in low light conditions can deliver artful images.

🚗Reversing Camera Mode & Intelligent Voice Assistant: This driving recorder dash cams will automatically show full rear view when the car reverse gear is engaged. The waterproof rear view camera will help you to park your car easily and safely. Simple commands can be executed through the intelligent voice assistant, for example, turn off recording, show pre-record... This driving recorder can achieve hands-free function, and the voice recognition rate is as high as 98%.

Under normal operation, if the following problems occur, please refer to the solution. (FAQ) Q: The recorder can't take pictures and video? A: Check whether the TF card has enough space and is locked. Q: Can't charge? A: The normal dash recorder has a built-in battery, which can be used for 3-5 minutes in an emergency. Because the battery will be exhausted during transportation, it needs to be charged for a period of time after receiving the recorder before it can be started. If it still cannot be turned on, then the car charger is probably damaged. Q: Why is the card full after a few days of use? A: You need to check whether the G-Sensor, Parking Monitor and Motion Detection functions are turned on, because the videos recorded by these three functions cannot be automatically overwritten. Q: Why does the rear camera not display and have no image? A: The reversing camera needs to be connected well before the power is turned on. It is recommended to insert it several times. There may be burrs in the production process, which may cause poor contact.
